narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned a whole new world of chemistry under the umbrella statistical mechanics. Mostly derivations and math, the class had some coding in it also.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This course is very interesting, though it lacks structure. There are no regular assignments, so it can be hard to stay on top of the material. There was not very much feedback or it made it hard to know where I stood in the class.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, if you are interested and willing to put in a lot self-motivated work. Otherwise, the exams will feel overwhelming.
